---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Cookie Policy | SDAP Precision Hardware";
const description = "";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} isHome=false>
    <main class="legal-container">
        <h1 class="legal-title">Cookie Policy</h1>
        <span class="legal-updated">Last Updated: March 2026</span>

        <div class="legal-content">
            <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
            <p>Cookies are text files placed on your computer or device to collect standard internet log information and visitor behavior. When you visit our portfolio, we may collect information regarding your interaction with our GSAP-driven galleries through cookies or similar technology.</p>
            
            <h2>2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
            <p>SDAP uses cookies in a range of ways to improve your experience on our website, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Ensuring smooth scroll performance and asset loading for high-resolution macro photography.</li>
                <li>Understanding how you navigate our hardware catalog.</li>
                <li>Remembering your interactions with our corporate B2B inquiry forms.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
            <p><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the fundamental operation of our digital infrastructure.</p>
            <p><strong>Analytical Cookies:</strong> These allow us to recognize and count visitors and see how they navigate our structural interfaces to optimize the global viewing experience.</p>

            <h2>4. Managing Cookies</h2>
            <p>You can adjust your browser policies to decline cookies. However, disabling all cookies may cause some smooth-scrolling animation features to degrade gracefully.</p>

            <h2>5. Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about our Cookie Policy, please contact our administrative team at <a href="mailto:privacy@jeansbutton.pro">privacy@jeansbutton.pro</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 S&D Asia Pacific Ltd (SDAP). All rights reserved.</p>
            <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
